import React from 'react'
import { Formik, Form, Field, ErrorMessage } from 'formik';

function CreatPost() {
    return (
        <div className="createPostPage">
            <Formik /*initialValues={} onSubmit={} validationSchema={}*/>
                <Form>
                    <label>Title:</label>
                    <Field 
                        id="inputCreatePost" 
                        name="title" 
                        placeholder="(Ex. Uma noite...)"
                    />
            </Form>
        </Formik>
        </div >
    )
}

export default CreatPost
